# Cloudflare Pages headers. NOTE: this file is platform config — it is NOT
# served, and vite.config.ts's precache plugin must keep excluding it from the
# service-worker manifest (a precached /_headers 404s and kills the offline
# install). No CSP: the pages carry deliberate inline boot scripts (theme
# before first paint), which a meaningful CSP would have to nonce — out of
# scope for a fully static, no-third-party site.
/*
  X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff
  Referrer-Policy: strict-origin-when-cross-origin
  Permissions-Policy: camera=(), microphone=(), geolocation=()
  X-Frame-Options: DENY
/assets/*
  Cache-Control: public, max-age=31536000, immutable
/sw.js
  Cache-Control: no-store
